---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About EDITH Dev Studio"
  description="Learn more about EDITH Dev Studio and its premium Windows-first desktop tools."
>
  <Navbar />

  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>EDITH Dev Studio</h1>
      <p class="legal-note">
        EDITH Dev Studio is the publisher brand behind Upscaler Studio and future premium Windows-first desktop products.
      </p>

      <section class="legal-block premium-panel">
        <h2>What the studio is building</h2>
        <p>
          The studio direction is focused on serious desktop software with stronger product presentation,
          cleaner commercial readiness, and a better user experience than disposable utility-grade tools.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-block premium-panel">
        <h2>Current focus</h2>
        <p>
          Upscaler Studio is the first featured product and is positioned around local AI upscaling,
          Windows-first workflows, and a premium product surface for image and video users.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-block premium-panel">
        <h2>Future direction</h2>
        <p>
          The website and studio identity are designed to support multiple products over time, not only a single release.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
